```
Each `@tracked` property is declared independently on its own line. You can have as many `@tracked` properties as needed — each one is independently reactive. Glimmer tracks which specific properties the template reads and only re-renders when those change.

```gjs
import Component from '@glimmer/component';
import { tracked } from '@glimmer/tracking';

export default class MatchFormatComponent extends Component {
