Initialize to `null` when the value is intentionally absent — like before a user makes a selection or before data is fetched. Always guard with `{{#if}}` before accessing properties on a nullable tracked value to avoid template errors.

```gjs
import Component from '@glimmer/component';
import { tracked } from '@glimmer/tracking';

export default class VenueComponent extends Component {
  @tracked venue = undefined;

  <template>
